title: Bucket with rounded rim motif

claims.preamble: The ornamental design for a bucket with rounded rim motif, as shown and described.

description: FIG. 1 is a front view of a bucket with rounded rim motif, the rear view being identical thereto;
FIG. 2 is a right side view thereof, the opposite side view being identical thereto;
FIG. 3 is top view thereof; and,
FIG. 4 is a bottom view thereof.
The bucket being shown with sleeves internal thereto in phantom lines that form no part of the claimed design.
